dct_description_sm: Map of Forked River (now Lacey Township), Ocean County, N.J. is from Woolman and Rose's Atlas of the New Jersey Coast, 1878, Plate 25. Map notes names of property owners and wooded land. Includes segment of Toms River and Waretown railroad line.
